# ============================================
# ✅ SAFE TO COMMIT:
# ============================================
# - Python scripts (.py)
# - JavaScript files (.js)
# - Configuration files (except .env)
# - Documentation (.md)
# - Docker configs (docker-compose.yml, Dockerfile)
# - MCP server code (not credentials)
# - Watcher scripts
# - Agent code
# ============================================
